2026-06-19  Qaaxaap  <1515784026@qq.com>

	* configure.ac: Add --with-lfspkg=DIR option and header check.
	Link against lfspkg static library for package database API.
	* src/Makefile.am: Add @LFSPKG_CPPFLAGS@ and @LFSPKG_LIBS@
	substitution variables for lfspkg integration.
	* src/cli.hpp: Declare cmd_upgrade().
	* src/cli.cpp: Implement cmd_install() with recursive dependency
	resolution, MAKEFS build execution via bash wrapper, and lfspkg
	package registration with automatic built_deps tracking.
	Implement cmd_rebuild() with --stale, --all, and per-package modes;
	stale detection uses lfspkg::find_stale_packages() to compare
	built_deps versions against currently-installed dependency versions.
	Cascade: after every rebuild, automatically rebuild newly-stale
	reverse dependencies until a fixed point is reached.
	Implement cmd_list() using lfspkg::PackageDB::list_packages().
	Implement cmd_upgrade() to compare installed versions against the
	repository index and upgrade out-of-date packages with full cascade.
	Add load_index_versions() helper that reads meta/index into a
	name→version map for version comparison.
	Add topo_sort() helper to order rebuilds with dependencies first.
	* ChangeLog: This file.
	* NEWS: Update for 0.2.1.

