2026-05-29  Qaaxaap  <1515784026@qq.com>

	* configure.ac: Bump version to 0.1.3.
	* src/makefs.hpp: New file.  Data structures for MAKEFS parser:
	SubPackage, Trigger, MakefsSpec.  Public API: parse_makefs() and
	parse_makefs_string().
	* src/makefs.cpp: New file.  Full MAKEFS parser implementation.
	Two-pass architecture: line-oriented state machine (TOP, HEREDOC,
	FUNCTION_BODY) collects raw variables and function bodies; then
	iterative variable expansion with circular reference detection
	(max depth 10).  Supports [package.X] sub-package sections,
	[trigger] sections, heredoc strings, backslash continuation,
	CRLF stripping, and shell function body collection.
	* tests/test_makefs.cpp: New file.  18 test cases: basic parsing,
	full multi-package example, variable expansion, heredoc, function
	bodies, brace expansion tolerance, backslash continuation,
	comments, duplicate keys, CRLF, and error conditions.
	* src/Makefile.am: Add makefs.cpp and makefs.hpp to qp_SOURCES.
	* tests/Makefile.am: Add test_makefs check program and TESTS entry.
	* NEWS: Update for 0.1.3.
	* ChangeLog: This file.

